title: Star Shine by Fredric Brown
description:
"Star Shine" is a 17-story Fredric Brown anthology published in paperback by Ballantine in 1956. The original hardback edition, titled "Angels and Spaceships," was published in 1954 by E.P. Dutton. 

Both volumes contain the exact same stories: Pattern; Placet Is a Crazy Place; Answer; Etaoin Shrdlu; Preposterous; Armageddon; Politeness; The Waveries; Reconciliation; The Hat Trick; Search; Letter to a Phoenix; Daisies; The Angelic Angleworm; Sentence; The Yehudi Principle; Solipsist.

Genre: Classic science fiction
